T1  - Natural Oligopolies: A Vertical Differentiation Model
AU  - Lahmandi-Ayed, Rim
Y1  - 2000/11/01
PY  - 2000
DA  - 2000/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/1468-2354.00092
T2  - International Economic Review
